Bottom_rated_topics_1.query:
q = load "${App.Datasets.SurveyQuestionResponsewithDetails_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = filter q by {{cell(View_Topics_by_1.selection, 0, "Filter").asEquality('Question_QuestionType')}}; q = filter q by 'ChoiceAndQuestionTopics_Topics_Topic_Name' is not null; q_no_choices = group q by ('Id', 'SurveyVersion_Survey_Id', 'SurveyVersionId', 'QuestionId', 'ChoiceAndQuestionTopics_Topics_Topic_Name'); q_no_choices = foreach q generate 'Id' , 'SurveyVersion_Survey_Id', 'SurveyVersionId', 'QuestionId', first('QuestionChoices_Name') as 'QuestionChoices_Name', 'ChoiceAndQuestionTopics_Topics_Topic_Name' as 'ChoiceAndQuestionTopics_Topics_Topic_Name', first('NumberValue') as 'NumberValue'; q_no_choices = filter q_no_choices by 'QuestionChoices_Name' is null; q = group q by ('Id', 'SurveyVersion_Survey_Id', 'SurveyVersionId', 'QuestionId', 'QuestionChoices_Name', 'ChoiceAndQuestionTopics_Topics_Topic_Name'); q = foreach q generate 'Id' , 'SurveyVersion_Survey_Id', 'SurveyVersionId', 'QuestionId', 'QuestionChoices_Name' as 'QuestionChoices_Name', 'ChoiceAndQuestionTopics_Topics_Topic_Name' as 'ChoiceAndQuestionTopics_Topics_Topic_Name', first('NumberValue') as 'NumberValue'; q = union q, q_no_choices; q = order q by ('SurveyVersion_Survey_Id' asc, 'SurveyVersionId' asc, 'QuestionId' asc, 'QuestionChoices_Name' asc); q = group q by ('Id', 'SurveyVersion_Survey_Id', 'SurveyVersionId', 'QuestionId', 'ChoiceAndQuestionTopics_Topics_Topic_Name'); q = foreach q generate 'Id' , 'SurveyVersion_Survey_Id', 'SurveyVersionId', 'QuestionId', 'ChoiceAndQuestionTopics_Topics_Topic_Name', {{cell(View_Topics_by_1.selection, 0, "Measure").asObject()}} first('NumberValue') as 'NumberValue'; q = group q by 'ChoiceAndQuestionTopics_Topics_Topic_Name'; q = foreach q generate 'ChoiceAndQuestionTopics_Topics_Topic_Name' as 'ChoiceAndQuestionTopics_Topics_Topic_Name',  {{cell(View_Topics_by_1.selection, 0, "Projection").asObject()}}; q = order q by {{cell(View_Topics_by_1.selection, 0, "Sort").asObject()}} asc;
q = limit q 20;
